{"tid":227309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警員涉瞞警車撞毁消防龍頭　妨礙司法罪不成立　官稱自招嫌疑","createTime":"2017-05-03T05:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T07:38:29.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59843f6d904ab939fbeda93540920f7899f637cd","tid":227309,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:40:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警員涉瞞警車撞毁消防龍頭　妨礙司法罪不成立　官稱自招嫌疑</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170502/s00001/d738962ddd4451c06411aa860cafceed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170502%2Fs00001%2Fd738962ddd4451c06411aa860cafceed.jpg&h=3261dd72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員譚永昌<br />\n<br />\n警員於去年8月駕駛警車時撞毁消防龍頭，卻向上級隱瞞事件，事後被控不小心駕駛及妨礙司法公正。裁判官早前裁定不小心駕駛罪表面證供不成立，今指雖然專家報告稱警車油漆痕和涉案水龍頭油漆的顏色及化學成分一致，控方未有直接證據證明是警員駛車撞毁消防龍頭，裁定其妨礙司法公正罪不成立，並獲賠一半訟費。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官今裁決時指出，閉路電視片段模糊不清，未能拍攝到水龍頭被撞經過和警車的車牌號碼，而警車油漆痕有與涉案水龍頭的相同油漆，但不足以證明到是警員譚永昌（41歲）駕車撞毁消防龍頭，故裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n辯方其後申請訟費，惟裁判官以譚在錄影會面中自招嫌疑為由，最終只批准他獲一半訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170502/s00001/1493720008384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170502%2Fs00001%2F1493720008384&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8qS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=722af702\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170502%2Fs00001%2F1493720008384&h=a230b3e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170502/s00001/1493720008384</a><br />\n<br />\n咁都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b9df71365a03d7ce24478a2c374cec5e59a5f9","tid":227309,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"一半訟費已經好撚多...."},{"pid":"efdbd16c1dfb821ea240ec5e83295ceed217b497